      "content": "i know i should ask my doctor but they're super hard to get a hold of and i'm just so exhausted right now. i've read online that melatonin is just a natural hormone and zolpidem is a sedative, so shouldn't they just work together to help me knock out? it seems like they're doing different things anyway so it shouldn't be that dangerous, right?",
