    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you but i'm literally at my breaking point here. i'm only taking a low dose of melatonin and i just want to know if it's actually physically dangerous. like is there a specific reason they shouldn't be taken together? if i just take a small amount of both to get through tonight, is that really going to cause a major issue or is it just the standard \"talk to your doctor\" warning? i just need a straight answer so i can sleep.",
